I"ö<p>For the last 3 years, IoT has been a term hyped to no end by the industry and the media (together with Big Data and Blockchain, amongst others). Hyped technology concepts are good because they create awareness outside of its starting niche community, but it also has the drawback of creating skepticism. IoT is no exception to this phenomenon, especially since many organization have invested significant amount of capital in the technology without delivering value back to their organisations.</p>
